; Promote sleep deprivation / thirst state from file-local to module-level
; so simulated_time_sleep.script can snapshot and restore them around the
; simulated advance. Without this, actor_on_update drain ticks that fire
; many times during the stepped advance inflate these values far beyond
; what vanilla (single-frame time jump) produces.

[actor_status_sleep]
last_sleep

[actor_status_thirst]
last_drink
